### Markup

The Calendar module can also be configured from HTML markup. The first step is to create a HTML element.

``` html
<div id="myCalendar" class="aui-calendar-content"></div>
```
Then, simply create an instance of Calendar and specify the `boundingBox` and `srcNodes`.

``` javascript
AUI().ready(
  'aui-calendar',
  function(A) {
    new A.Calendar(
      {
        boundingBox: '#myCalendar',
        srcNode: '#myCalendar .aui-calendar-content'
      }
    ).render();
  }
);
```

